cs.DC, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with distributed systems and their implementation using Petri nets. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper involves formalisation and precise characterisation of system specifications. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as Petri nets are a formalism used in programming languages. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper deals with system specifications and their implementation. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper deals with distributed systems and their behaviour.
